{"type":"message","id":"6c0af72c","parentId":"69d7e3ea","timestamp":"2026-05-07T20:01:20.500Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8c4t9ftn5r98_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"mcp-usemcp-usemcp-use\nOpinionated MCP Framework for TypeScript (@modelcontextprotocol/sdk compatible) - Build MCP Agents, Clients and Servers with support for ChatGPT Apps, Code Mode, OAuth, Notifications, Sampling, Observability and more.Opinionated MCP Framework for TypeScript (@modelcontextprotocol/sdk compatible) - Build MCP Agents, Clients and Servers with support for ChatGPT Apps, Code Mode, OAuth, Notifications, Sampling, Observability and more.Opinionated MCP Framework for TypeScript (@modelcontextprotocol/sdk compatible) - Build MCP Agents, Clients and Servers with support for ChatGPT Apps, Code Mode, OAuth, Notifications, Sampling, Observability and more.\nVersion 1.27.0 published 2026-05-06 by GitHub Actions\nMaintainers: pzullo pederzh tonxxd zane.npm\nKeywords: MCP mcp-use Model Context Protocol ChatGPT Apps Code Mode OAuth Notifications Sampling SDK mcp-ui mcp-inspector ai utility typescript\nhttps://npm.im/mcp-use\n\nmcp-proxymcp-proxymcp-proxy\nA TypeScript SSE proxy for MCP servers that use stdio transport.A TypeScript SSE proxy for MCP servers that use stdio transport.A TypeScript SSE proxy for MCP servers that use stdio transport.\nVersion 6.4.6 published 2026-04-13 by GitHub Actions\nMaintainers: punkpeye\nKeywords: MCP SSE proxy\nhttps://npm.im/mcp-proxy\n\n@debugmcp/mcp-debugger@debugmcp/mcp-debugger@debugmcp/mcp-debugger\nStep-through debugging MCP server for LLMsStep-through debugging MCP server for LLMsStep-through debugging MCP server for LLMs\nVersion 0.20.0 published 2026-03-30 by debugmcpdev\nMaintainers: debugmcpdev\nhttps://npm.im/@debugmcp/mcp-debugger"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":550,"aggregated":"mcp-usemcp-usemcp-use\nOpinionated MCP Framework for TypeScript (@modelcontextprotocol/